th Ireland an unexpected birthplace"--cPublisher's Web site.  a16 23 0aTrials (Heresy)zIrelandxHistoryyTo 1500. 0aTrials (Witchcraft)zIrelandxHistoryyTo 1500. 0aIrelandxChurch historyy600-1500.  aBR 794 C35 2015hUAAU-Bi0162035241635  aBR 794 C35 2015wLCc1i0162034578912lON_SHELFmUAAUGp$150.00rYsYtBOOKu2/19/2015  aBR 794 C35 2015wLCc1i32860001071959lON_SHELFmBURMANrYsYtBOOKu8/26/201501ahttp://id.loc.gov/authorities/names/no2014078338bhttp://viaf.org/viaf/308771976